{
  "chapter": 4,
  "chapter_summary": "春日小镇长街上，楚留香进入崔大娘老店易容成白胡子老头，胡铁花则在茶馆被伙计索账，又被一名柔弱少女以付账和哭诉诱上马车。四名少女把他带到江边，声明上次用迷药擒他，此番要凭真功夫较量。她们以短兵器、灵活身形和涂油脱身之法围攻胡铁花，并透露已识破楚留香易容，另雇人对付他。楚留香及时现身，少女们跳江逃走。事后楚留香说明袭击者是铁剑先生逐出的弟子，四名少女背后疑有庞大组织支援；他决定再次改装，与胡铁花分开暗中保护。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我们到那里去坐坐好不好?",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "好。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "你去吧。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你呢?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "我要先到对面那家铺子去一趟。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "这个老小子又在玩什么花样?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你这个老王八蛋，为什么要把自己弄得像这种鬼样子?",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cha_guan_huo_ji",
      "speaker_name": "茶馆伙计",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "老太爷，在我们这块吃东西的客人，都是付过账才走的，老太爷，你说对不对?",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_you_yuan_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "幽怨小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "我替你付账，你跟我走。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_you_yuan_xiao_gu_niang",
      "text": "我不跟你走，你也一样要替我付账的。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_you_yuan_xiao_gu_niang",
      "text": "这一次好像轮到你要听我的话了。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_you_yuan_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "幽怨小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "求求你，跟我回去吧!婆婆和孩子都病得那么重，你就不能回去看看他们么?你知不知道我找你找得有多苦?",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_you_yuan_xiao_gu_niang",
      "text": "想不到你原来是我的老婆。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_you_yuan_xiao_gu_niang",
      "text": "亲爱的好老婆，你究竟想把我带到哪里去?",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_si_ge_xiao_gu_niang",
      "text": "其实不管你要把我带到哪里都没关系。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_si_ge_xiao_gu_niang",
      "text": "反正你已经是我的老婆，总不会谋杀亲夫的。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_si_ge_xiao_gu_niang",
      "text": "不知道从哪里才能弄点酒来喝喝，就算酒里有迷药，我也照样会喝下去。",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_ge_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "四个小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "上次我们是用迷药把你逮到的，你落在我们手里，心里一定不服气。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_ge_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "四个小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "在你那个狗窝里，那个又奸又鬼的楚留香趁我们不注意，占了我们一点便宜，你心里一定认为我们全是好欺负的人。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_ge_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "四个小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "所以这一次我们就要凭真功夫跟你动手了，要你输得口服心服。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_ge_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "四个小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "我们只问你，这一次你若败在我们手里，你准备怎么办?",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_si_ge_xiao_gu_niang",
      "text": "如果你们一定要凭真功夫跟我动手，我也只好奉陪。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_si_ge_xiao_gu_niang",
      "text": "如果我输了，随便你们要怎么办就怎么办，我绝对没有第二句话说。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_yan_jing_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "大眼睛小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "如果你觉得这是件很好玩的事，那么我保证你很快就会觉得不好玩了。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_yan_jing_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "大眼睛小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "你不必等了。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_yan_jing_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "大眼睛小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "那个忽然变成了老头子的楚留香不会来的。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_da_yan_jing_xiao_gu_niang",
      "text": "什么老头子?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_da_yan_jing_xiao_gu_niang",
      "text": "哪个老头子?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_yan_jing_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "大眼睛小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "你以为我们不知道?",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_tui_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "长腿小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "我们正好亲眼看见他走进崔大娘的店里去，又正好亲眼看见那个老头走出来，跟你坐在一起吃包子。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_tui_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "长腿小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "难道你还以为我们看不出他就是楚留香?难道你以为我们都是猪?",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chang_tui_xiao_gu_niang",
      "text": "你们怎么知道那个老头子不会来?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_ge_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "四个小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "因为我们早就准备好几个人去对付他了，如果现在他还没有死，运气已经很不错。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_wen_rou_xiao_gu_niang",
      "text": "你们要他死?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_wen_rou_xiao_gu_niang",
      "text": "万一他不是楚留香怎么办?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_rou_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "温柔小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "那么就算我们杀错了人。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_rou_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "温柔小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "杀错个把人，也是很平常的事。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_wen_rou_xiao_gu_niang",
      "text": "那实在太平常了，就算杀错七八十个人也没什么关系。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_wen_rou_xiao_gu_niang",
      "text": "只不过以后你们想起这种事的时候，晚上也许会睡不着的，那些冤鬼说不定就会去拜访拜访你们。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_rou_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "温柔小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "你放心，我们晚上一向睡得很好。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_si_ge_xiao_gu_niang",
      "text": "就算你们睡着了，也说不定会梦见那些冤鬼在脱你们的裤子。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_ge_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "四个小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "放你的屁。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_si_ge_xiao_gu_niang",
      "text": "放屁?谁在放屁?",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_si_ge_xiao_gu_niang",
      "text": "如果有人在放屁，那个人绝对不是我，我从来都不会放屁的。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_ge_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "四个小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "不可以，千万不可以。",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "一个大男人怎么可以骗小姑娘?你明明比谁都会放屁，怎么能说不会?你不会谁会?天下难道还有比你更会放屁的人?",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我就知道你不会死的，我这一辈子都没有见过运气比你更好的人，你怎么会死!",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "快抓住一个。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "只要抓住一个就好。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "这么漂亮的小姑娘，为什么要把自己弄得像油鸡一样?为什么要把自己全身上下都抹上一层油?",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "如果我将来娶了老婆，只要她身上有一点油，我就用大板子打她的屁股。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "的确有个人该打屁股。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "惟一应该被打屁股的这个人就是你。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "对，我应该打屁股，我连一个都没有抓住。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "可是你呢?你是干什么的?你又不是没有手，你自己为什么不来抓?",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "你为什么不能用点脑筋想想，像我这么有身份的人，怎么能去抓女人的腿?",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "你还有件事更该打屁股。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "什么事?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "刚才你骗她们跟你说话的时候，你就有好几次机会可以把她们制住，最少也可以制住其中两个。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "她们的招式间明明已经有了破绽，你却像瞎子一样看不见。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我怎么会看不见?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "只不过我虽然不像你这么有身份，多少也有一点身份，怎么能往一个光溜溜的大姑娘那种地方出手!",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你怎么知道那时候我有机会出手的?难道那时候你就已经来了?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "如果我没有来，我怎么会看见?",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "如果我没有看见，我怎么会知道?",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "好，好，好，好极了!原来你早就来了，早就躲在一边偷偷的看着。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你的好朋友随时都可能被人一刀割断脖子，你却躲在那里偷看女人的大腿，你惭愧不惭愧?",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "我惭愧，我本来实在非常惭愧。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "可是我忽然想到如果你是我，恐怕现在还在看，还没有出来。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "一想到这一点，我就连一点惭愧的意思都没有了。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你怎么这么了解我?难道你是我肚子里的蛔虫?",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "老实说，我自己也觉得我实在应该打屁股，居然会让她们全都溜了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "可是你呢?你为什么不把刚才对付你的那些人抓住一两个?却把他们的帽子带了回来，难道你能从这几顶帽子上看出他们的来历?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "我根本用不着盘问他们的来历。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "为什么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "因为我本来就认得他们。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "他们都是铁剑先生在上一次清理门户时被逐出的弟子，在江湖中流落了几年，志气渐渐消磨，渐渐变得什么事都肯做了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "他们知不知道这个白胡子老头是楚香帅?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "大概也不会知道，否则他们恐怕就不会接这笔生意了。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "就在你走出崔大娘的老店，坐下来吃东西的时候，她们就能找到人来对付你!",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "这四个小丫头的本事倒真不小。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "也许她们自己并没有这么大的本事，可是这附近一带一定有她们的人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "这些人的神通一定都不小，所以她们无论要干什么都方便得很。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "所以我们还是应该分开来走，而且我还要先走一步。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "为什么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "因为这个白胡子老头已经被认出来了，已经没法子再混下去。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "所以你又要去找那位崔大娘?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "难道她也是位精于易容的高手，我怎么从来都没有听说过?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "你没有听说过的事本来就多得很。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "这次你准备要她把你变成什么样子?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "我不能告诉你。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "也许还是个小老头，也许是个大腹贾，也许是条山东大汉，也许是个文弱书生，总之是个你从未见过的人，甚至连我自己都没有见过，只不过我一定会在你附近的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "我这么做，都是为了你的安全，如果连你都不知道那个人是我，别人当然更看不出来了，这样子我才好保护你。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "我对你实在比你对你的妈还要好得多。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "你笑什么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我忽然想到了一件非常好笑的事。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我忽然想到你如果要扮成一个大姑娘，说不定有很多男人都会看上你的，如果其中有个采花大盗，那就更好玩了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 386
    }
